"description": "总结常见应用层协议所使用的运输层协议（TCP/UDP）及其端口号，强调该表格的重要性，建议学生背诵以应对考试。"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 803.84,\n    "end_time": 850.6,\n    "knowledge_point": "课程总结与练习题预告",\n    "description": "总结本节课内容，布置课后练习题，并预告下一节课程，鼓励学生复习巩固知识。"\n  }\n]'}], 'reasoning_content': '', 'role': 'assistant'}, 'finish_reason': 'stop'}]}, 'usage': {'total_tokens': 16721, 'input_tokens_details': {'text_tokens': 15791}, 'output_tokens': 930, 'input_tokens': 15791, 'output_tokens_details': {'text_tokens': 930}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'cached_tokens': 0}}, 'request_id': 'e3e41846-3edc-47ad-b0a6-e74be2364532'}
