scription": "总结常见应用层协议所使用的运输层协议（TCP/UDP）及其端口号，强调该表格的重要性及需记忆的内容。"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 803.84,\n    "end_time": 850.6,\n    "knowledge_point": "课程总结与练习题预告",\n    "description": "总结本节课内容，布置课后练习题，并公布答案，最后鼓励学生并预告下一节课程。"\n  }\n]'}], 'reasoning_content': '', 'role': 'assistant'}, 'finish_reason': 'stop'}]}, 'usage': {'total_tokens': 16713, 'input_tokens_details': {'text_tokens': 15791}, 'output_tokens': 922, 'input_tokens': 15791, 'output_tokens_details': {'text_tokens': 922}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'cached_tokens': 0}}, 'request_id': '05229969-58e2-4e82-b903-09f8a42a5776'}
