CP协议用于自动获取IP地址，避免手工配置，解决IP冲突问题，并通过“CP=分配”帮助记忆其功能。"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 768.64,\n    "end_time": 803.84,\n    "knowledge_point": "应用层协议总结表",\n    "description": "总结常见应用层协议所使用的运输层协议（TCP/UDP）及其端口号，强调该表格的重要性，建议背诵以应对考试。"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 803.84,\n    "end_time": 850.6,\n    "knowledge_point": "课程总结与练习题预告",\n    "description": "总结本节课内容，布置课后练习题，并预告下一节课程，鼓励学生复习巩固。"\n  }\n]'}], 'reasoning_content': '', 'role': 'assistant'}, 'finish_reason': 'stop'}]}, 'usage': {'total_tokens': 16787, 'input_tokens_details': {'text_tokens': 15791}, 'output_tokens': 996, 'input_tokens': 15791, 'output_tokens_details': {'text_tokens': 996}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'cached_tokens': 0}}, 'request_id': 'e27f628a-defe-4309-8ea1-73e01491757a'}
